&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Celonis is the global leader in Process Intelligence and the pioneer of Process Mining technology. As one of the world’s fastest-growing enterprise SaaS companies, we are changemakers pushing the boundaries of what’s possible. We invest heavily in advanced AI capabilities—specifically our Process Intelligence Graph—to turn data insights into immediate business action. We believe there is a massive opportunity to unlock global productivity and sustainability by placing intelligence at the core of every business process. Join our mission to make processes work for people, companies, and the planet.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Team&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Celonis Business Apps IT is a team of product enthusiasts and data engineers that focuses on developing best-in class composable AI solutions in the domain of System Transformations (migrations such as SAP ECC to S/4, introduction of new software, system landscape consolidation, etc.). Business Apps are purpose-built solutions created for a specific line of business, addressing most impactful pain points in their respective domain. The solutions are best practice examples of how Celonis is used in new, innovative ways that push the boundaries of our platform. The team has a great balance of technical skills to build solutions paired with a customer focus and product management mindset to create meaningful products widely adopted across our customer base.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The Role&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We&#39;re looking for a hybrid between a product manager and an engineer. Someone who can sit with a customer, understand a transformation pain point, and then go design and build the solution together with the rest of the team rather than handing it off. You&#39;ll operate in a fast-paced, ambiguous environment where shipping quickly matters more than perfect process, and where the line between &quot;designing the product&quot; and &quot;building the product&quot; is intentionally blurry. You get hands-on: prototyping on the platform, wiring up data, composing AI-driven applications, and iterating directly with the people who&#39;ll use them.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You&#39;ll be at the frontier of how Celonis reimagines enterprise system transformation. Turning a bold vision into working products that customers adopt. If you&#39;re energized by owning something end-to-end, moving fast, and being measured by what you ship rather than what you spec, this is for you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;The work you&#39;ll do&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Your mission is to make the vision of AI powered system transformation a reality. Building products that turn the cutting edge capabilities of the Celonis Process Intelligence platform from strategy into solutions customers run on.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build and ship purpose-built but flexible solutions that span the full enterprise modernization journey&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverage the most cutting-edge capabilities of the Celonis platform and compose them into coherent, deployable solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work hands-on with frontier AI development tools that plug natively into the platform, using them to accelerate how you build, enrich, and deploy solutions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Move fluidly between customer, prototype, and production: discover the pain point, build the thing, put it in front of users, and iterate fast&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive all steps within the product development lifecycle from ideation to product development to scaling solutions across all Celonis customers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with platform product managers, engineers and partners to influence the underlying Celonis capabilities your solutions depend on&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with GTM, UX, and customers to ensure what you build actually gets adopted and scales across the customer base

